{"type": "article", "id": 24890, "title": "你已经腻了哪些武侠片的梗？这有 25 个", "description": "一个孤独求败的高手，一个倾国倾城的美人", "date": "2016-04-04T08:27:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 25753, "name": "武侠片"}], "category": 3, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 36, "praise_count": 229, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021140500l72IE3nMsHSkjWf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">好奇心研究所的微博（@好奇心研究所）和微信公众号（ID：QLab42）全面上线啦，关注就可以与所长亲密接触。  <br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1. 魔教。魔教长老的女儿。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114039Au92Qhtq8goPTpi7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54960317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2. 正派。正派中的小人。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114039Mk54ezwQjmZ2u3Ad.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66521739\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3. 一个孤独求败的上一代高手。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114040jNA3MyKs1ZUVYiTJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4. 一个倾国倾城的上一代美人。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114040pwEXJMxGbTi9Kmoh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76909091\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5. 一本失传已久的武林秘籍。一本叫人割丁丁的武林邪典。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114041pKISvYAG1HqZrfmd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>6. 一只天赋异禀的宠物。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114041ZnqBzMhI2YWOTy5L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>7. 灭门惨案。血海深仇。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114042m6tnxkMTCJW1V7Bc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.495\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>8. 天将降大任于是人也，必先受很多冤屈。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021140420DmuJlN4Qb2VET1n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>9. 女主很美很爱男主。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114042O6E7F89DUjYtMd1q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><b>10. 金庸的女主一定皮肤很白很白。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021140438YlUARZBWDVzi940.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74257426\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>11. 还要有几个活泼可爱/温婉动人/但不如女主美的红颜知己。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070211404342mASzODuwUlhaGW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67398649\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>12. 胸部明显的女扮男装。  </b><b style=\"text-align: center;\">  </b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114044qSZQPxDvN47cinWJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>13. 误服春药。明明可以用手/洗冷水……非要……</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114044CxLFVK9GbzP2AgrX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60094637\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>14. 摆阵的道士/和尚。  <br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114044gUiPnk0TmG42EqVX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>15. 抱团的恶人。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114045rcWgYfSyUZin2IBC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>16. 追杀。掉下悬崖。N 年以后。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114045z8WwupXD05oP7x1F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55517241\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>17. 冰山/老顽童/吃货师父。  </b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114046XpQtJ3uLxVd9ByWe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>18. 可爱的小师妹。小白脸师弟。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114046GY59tD3sek1Zc6aQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66521739\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>19. 酒馆、客栈、青楼。打群架。交流情报。艳遇。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114047axMdQ2SZrytW0pgz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>20. 一处人间仙境。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114047OPgW9qvYZut6FoRd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>21. 一种没有解药的毒药。一种能治百病的解药。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114048RT1UaKyZg8qfXHA2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73669065\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>22. 一个人轻功很好。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114048M1F3RX7A2jkWLEbG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.42708333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>23. 钱是怎么来的？</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114048Vlzo0qpTDsnwHCUx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68364611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>24. 打太监。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021140495hzp1Y83sqkDVnrt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66551724\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>25. 打外国人。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114049T4izCkN9IhnSY2fe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/labs.html\" target=\"_blank\"><em>好奇心研究所</em></a><em>是好奇心日报的一个调查栏目，这是一个探讨各种生活方式问题的互动平台，它针对的可能是生活方式的变化和潮流，也可能是某个品牌的服务。你可以在这里投票、吐槽、表明态度。</em>  <br></p>\n\n"}